{"tid":1361470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係土生土長元朗人，我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T05:42:09.000Z","uid":140595,"like":159,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"44724cd164e317e2d8cb33cbe6dae6ca5475a410","tid":1361470,"uid":140595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">入正題前，<strong>謹此 向上環、元朗既戰友同記者致敬</strong>；願受傷既早日康復、被捕既立即被釋放、撤控。</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n星期日我喺上環前線睇到眼火爆，之後係干諾道中忍唔住爆喊。<br />\n<br />\n但係喊都冇用，<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋要好好諗清楚點樣反擊</span>。<br />\n<br />\n我喺元朗生活左二十幾年。<br />\n黑社會出嚟打人好正常。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係黑社會打完人，警察唔止坐視不理，竟然可以警黑一家搭哂膊頭，仲要置市民同救護員性命於不顧。</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢一樣野先係令人最撚嬲，我地應該要逼到警黑兩方勢力再無後退之路，以還元朗戰友一個公道。<br />\n<br />\n但我哋要針對嘅唔係班圍村佬，<br />\n而係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作</span></strong>呢樣野。<br />\n呢件事係不論藍絲同黃絲都唔會反對嘅事，<br />\n我地就有最大既民意去做我地想做既野！<br />\n警隊唔應該係政府同黑社會既棋子！<br />\n<br />\n入村復仇有乜野意義？<br />\n我地入去鄉黑嘅地頭，但又唔熟路，<br />\n唔通要重演21號晚元朗站咁？<br />\n同班圍村佬結怨，只會令我地再多個敵人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔入去，唔係代表驚咗佢哋</span>，<br />\n反正我哋班後生乜都冇，有乜好驚。<br />\n但唔好忘記，我哋係長期抗爭。<br />\n任何嘅人命傷亡我哋都唔會想見到。<br />\n呢場運動，一個都不能少。<br />\n所以我哋要諗清楚目標同埋方向。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>行動最緊要係成功同埋有效，<br />\n而唔係發洩。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋拆完祠堂，其實班鄉黑都有保險賠。<br />\n政府或者中聯辦隨時比筆錢佢哋翻新祠堂，<br />\n咁樣我哋咪變咗送大禮？<br />\n咁樣值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n我哋可以做到更多野，去宣洩我哋嘅不滿。<br />\n就好似針對住嗰日警局拉閘，我哋可以包圍警署。<br />\n又或者因為遊行人數多，而迫爆大馬路、教育路同安寧路，呢三條元朗最主要嘅幹道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>令元朗全區癱瘓。</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋嘅目標係要逼政府表態。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一場成功嘅運動，係要哂民意，<br />\n勇武，同和理非。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n依加連政府部門都遍地開花，警察亦開始有人動搖。我哋更加要好好拉攏呢班人，<br />\n壯大自己士氣，煲大個民意。<br />\n而且經過元朗一伇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有好多港豬甚至藍絲都劍指政府，支持成立獨立調查委員會。</strong></span><br />\n所以我哋唔應該作出無謂嘅犧牲，係要同個政府鬥長命。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不割蓆，不篤灰。<br />\n齊上齊落，不撤不散。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，攬炒巴都一早講咗我哋要主力攻「警黑一家，警黑合作」。<br />\n【 緊急】集中火力攻「警黑一家，警黑合作」輿論戰！唔可以俾政府同黑社會割席！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1341889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1341889</a><br />\n<br />\n其他相關文章：<br />\n<br />\n[遍地開花] 跨 部 門 公 務 員 致 香 港 人 的 公 開 信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359384</a><br />\n<br />\n【聽原居民講】727元朗行動，唔好拆祠堂！唔好拆祠堂！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359437</a><br />\n<br />\n圍村土生土長，想同大家分析圍村生態同地勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361067</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span> </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAZyW8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAZyW8Q.png&h=6bbdedcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e86dfa80778011dc36767d47c3bc4d798e3a93c5","tid":1361470,"uid":150742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:18:49.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"1a969ac90dfbccfc41a1f2f9c7e3e2a627f45d95","tid":1361470,"uid":140595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/24/232018_c49f1ac7ff9950c51c3f016428a57de1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F24%2F232018_c49f1ac7ff9950c51c3f016428a57de1.png&h=49080207&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62ab4d545040c5cc4b00296fb9f3107791ae387a","tid":1361470,"uid":143441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d4fdfdaefef48d67783f21cba66582dcb55ed68","tid":1361470,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:21:27.000Z","msg":"我可以攬住你<br />\n放心係我身上喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805e0671a951eb67b290713985b2758d05dc200f","tid":1361470,"uid":8116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c665d76d7c40e30d2b84cf75ac18634d2a7fea2","tid":1361470,"uid":28257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:22:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">重點：迫爆大馬路、教育路同安寧路</span>"},{"pid":"8c85b53b2603b59a803f10747a8f57c8d9dd140e","tid":1361470,"uid":3171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:22:35.000Z","msg":"個個藍絲都話白衫打得好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149a79129491a2b2f3b79fc5dbab8fe85f16fa01","tid":1361470,"uid":274847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cffd5f984fb5f03d08c632950b73a6ecab413c1f","tid":1361470,"uid":231692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"804edee0fdc2043dd309b3bd40fc7a14a3c2a13a","tid":1361470,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"cb644e4ebc6b30bd316026c535bad5ce72ea6ffc","tid":1361470,"uid":231692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8953b80de8b43ed0aaafb1130320459ad00048f2","tid":1361470,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"425fbf0350d9ed3d807f7a8f1e3f211ddca8e53f","tid":1361470,"uid":78769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"覺得唔需要入村，你入咗村又點，啲人冇記認，最後只會同白衫軍一樣變咗無差別攻擊，有啲人仲要唔係原居民，出邊搬入去。咁做你自己都接受唔到啦吓話"},{"pid":"731fd837f0440ed29f1c65f22c364f3ef5a9969a","tid":1361470,"uid":45579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1c0b0ad6fe24afaa6ab3f7ac89a4d842cf697ff7","tid":1361470,"uid":119648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a4cf18827d6ee724ab1501a60cdba3ff9c7f8ee","tid":1361470,"uid":162731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da44e6f86dc4c319038ece54f75582df1b0611de","tid":1361470,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56de6746a9105079b30b1c402e78164be0c945ef","tid":1361470,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:26:44.000Z","msg":"支持！！"},{"pid":"e280d63b8e40500f562e3a29168cb82fd619d1b7","tid":1361470,"uid":258236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">開槍喎唔係唔理啊嘛</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">728中上環遊行！！<br />\n元朗重要，上環同樣重要</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1361287/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1361287/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n728上環公海 - <a href=\"http://t.me/sw728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0C2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=c8b1ffc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sw728</a><br />\nchannel - <a href=\"http://t.me/sw728update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728update&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0C2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=74087565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/sw728update</a><br />\n文宣 - <a href=\"https://t.me/sw728promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw728promo&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0C2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=6697ad5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sw728promo</a>"},{"pid":"511fb184823d08247355b41554e2497da48f9032","tid":1361470,"uid":37055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:27:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d28cb9ef4d2c54204c9ad278253fd2b84177781d","tid":1361470,"uid":8116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:28:38.000Z","msg":"今日好多人都已經出黎表態支持我地，<br />\n點樣借助呢個優勢。 <br />\n請所有想入村既勇武派唸下"},{"pid":"efeeb3dc8c42afbec136097b53877de0538e99e3","tid":1361470,"uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dab359ab2bc3575d4b2aead9cf03d4796ea71da","tid":1361470,"uid":8116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:29:56.000Z","msg":"拆完祠堂 只會增加仇恨<br />\n事情沒完沒了"},{"pid":"8a1e69284046ece5796421f9f826cb4131685c84","tid":1361470,"uid":286564,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"點解會批7.27<br />\n農曆 係 六月廿五<br />\n日值月破 即六月最凶果日<br />\n凡破日 諸事皆不宜<br />\n愚昧再卜算出四個字<br />\n魚死網破<br />\n趟若愚昧卜算相近，即兩邊皆損<br />\n港共政府&amp;黑警就是大贏家<br />\n況誰是魚，誰是網？<br />\n説不定<br />\n<br />\n希望各位再再再三思索<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑不如警察<br />\n不會思慮留手<br />\n黑警又擺明企係佢地果邊<br />\n<br />\n其實最賤就是黑警<br />\n反而發夢去圍警署<br />\n要佢交待無警時份<br />\n直播新聞明明拍到白衣人手持武器都話見唔到？<br />\n新聞片+自拍片都影到不下幾十個打人的暴徒有容有貌<br />\n點解唔去捉人？<br />\n爲何群眾去警署報警，反而落閘龜縮？<br />\n<br />\n希望各位有智之士不要中港共政府陷阱。"},{"pid":"0877e8a49db49e981c5809e101fe3464e5a3daad","tid":1361470,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5b90298f08e3986582019c1af02e39d09cb7c33","tid":1361470,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗咁緊張<br />\n基本上上次係中聯辦吹大雞先咁多人<br />\n今時今日吹得雞就一定會走漏風聲<br />\n<br />\n好多住村既人都不齒村入邊d黑社會<br />\n停車場 飯堂養道友 兵器庫 紅油場<br />\n<br />\n你話反鄉黑都無謂<br />\n因為知無可能根治<br />\n所以你反警黑合作 保護元朗市民就最好"},{"pid":"86150f047455f9e5f0361c4a4fb180c82599cf18","tid":1361470,"uid":140595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWsD8ke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWsD8ke.png&h=c1f7c7de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1ae44ab974860a4785be045d21b3dc28e23e24a","tid":1361470,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b943c37a65a627ebd463a7eb2cc69018548501aa","tid":1361470,"uid":258905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:33:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bda9c5a64ae7c11a759e713e9b8449195b1c4b3","tid":1361470,"uid":18596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:35:02.000Z","msg":"同意樓主，香港人加油！"},{"pid":"cb5ae68270d6cd4b6ec794211b829e4bba274700","tid":1361470,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:39:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"197c76f4b3dc82dcadf1c1ec8c47efd2ea11ee42","tid":1361470,"uid":288719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"驚到時有人擺d鬼混入，所以如果隔離左右太激進，要㩒住佢，大定要忍住唔好比人挑釁到，    一定要安全至上<br />\n一個都不能少呀！"},{"pid":"48111bea5bf3508a59d3f496e06ae03c6aea84e0","tid":1361470,"uid":185960,"like":0,"